room_title: Escape room "Mission Moscow" by Trapped RGV in Harlingen
room_description: The year is 1983. The Cold War is in full effect. The USSR has nuclear weapons aimed at the US, and the countdown clock has begun. President Reagan called upon your team of secret spies to save the US, but you were captured. Blindfolded & handcuffed your team now has 1 hour to break free, then find & dismantle the nuclear weapon. You are our only hope. Can you save the free world?
